H. Weeke, Plaintiff in Error, v. Kirke Monroe, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to' a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Escambia. H. Weeke, in pro. per., for Plaintiff in Error; Kirke Monroe, in pro. per., for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed by order of the Court.
